OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome early
OL,6,Fevening bright spells possible in the
OL,7,Fsouth before cloud and rain in the
OL,8,Fnorthwest, this heavy at times,
OL,9,Fspreads to all parts through the
OL,10,Fevening. Breezy, especially on coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy to start, gradually
OL,13,Fturning brighter from the west as rain
OL,14,Fslowly clears away eastwards. A chance
OL,15,Fof showers for a time in the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
