OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,6,Fwinds Sunday and Monday, with some
OL,7,Frain spreading east but also some
OL,8,Fdrier spells. Likely becoming dry
OL,9,FTuesday with light winds and sunny
OL,10,Fspells. Temperatures a little above
OL,11,Faverage.
